data.description: You'll love the open floor plan with cathedral ceilings, spacious rooms and plenty of natural light! This home is move-in ready and has recently been painted throughout along with updated lighting. Large eat-in kitchen has new stainless steel appliances. The main bedroom offers plenty of space with its own bathroom. The lower level was professionally finished including a family room, bathroom and two additional bedrooms. Outside enjoy the fenced in back yard from the covered deck! If resort-style living is what your looking for...come check out the community pool, big wheel track, soccer fields, club house, walking trails and open spaces. Come take a look before it is gone!
